// H√†m t√≠nh t·ªïng n∆∞·ªõc ƒë√£ d√πng d·ª±a tr√™n m·ª©c n∆∞·ªõc gi·∫£m d·∫ßn
function calcWaterUsage(days) {
    var cutoff = new Date();
    cutoff.setDate(cutoff.getDate() - days);
    var filtered = dbData.filter(function(d) {
        if (!d) return false;
        var ts = d.timestamp ? new Date(d.timestamp) : null;
        return ts && ts >= cutoff;
    }).sort(function(a, b) {
        return new Date(a.timestamp || a.date) - new Date(b.timestamp || b.date);
    });

    var usage = 0;
    var prev = null;
    filtered.forEach(function(d) {
        var val = Number(d.water || d.waterLevel || 0);
        if (prev !== null && val < prev) {
            usage += (prev - val);
        }
        prev = val;
    });
    return usage;
}

